            >
              MD, Metabolic Health
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--charcoal)] mb-2">
            Dr. Amelia Hayes
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Board-certified physician specializing in metabolic health and
            weight management with over 15 years of experience in internal
