            >
              Bariatric Surgery
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--charcoal)] mb-2">
            Dr. Olivia Bennett
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Skilled bariatric surgeon with a compassionate approach,
            specializing in minimally invasive techniques and comprehensive
            support.
          </p>
        </div>
